examples: It is too early for us to conclude anything.
Es demasiado pronto para que podamos concluir algo.
What do you conclude from that?
The report concluded (that) the cheapest option was to close the laboratory.
El informe concluyó (que) la opción más barata era cerrar el laboratorio.
He concluded from their remarks that they were not in favour of the plan.
De sus comentarios concluyó que no estaban a favor del plan.
